OL,3,CJannik Sinner defends Wimbledon title
OL,4,Cafter battling to defeat Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FJannik Sinner has fought off a
OL,8,Fdifficult challenge from Alexander
OL,9,FZverev to successfully defend his
OL,10,FWimbledon title.
OL,12,FFresh from winning his first grand
OL,13,Fslam crown at the French Open last
OL,14,Fmonth, Zverev shrugged off a poor
OL,15,Frecent record against Sinner to claim
OL,16,Fthe first set.
OL,18,FOn Sunday, Sinner managed to secure a
OL,19,F6-7 (7) 7-6 (2) 6-3 6-4 victory and a
OL,20,Ffifth major crown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
