PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783923682
OL,3,CJannik Sinner defends Wimbledon title
OL,4,Cafter battling to defeat Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FAfter only two break points in two-and-
OL,13,Fthree-quarter hours, another then
OL,14,Farrived in the next game, and Sinner
OL,15,Fsomehow recovered from a slip of his
OL,16,Fown mid-point to convert the
OL,17,Fopportunity, prompting Zverev to fling
OL,18,Fhis racket angrily to the turf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
