PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783923682
OL,3,CJannik Sinner defends Wimbledon title
OL,4,Cafter battling to defeat Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FThe gusting wind became an increasing
OL,8,Ffactor as the shadows lengthened
OL,9,Facross Centre Court during the fourth
OL,10,Fset.
OL,12,FSinner has only ever lost to Alcaraz
OL,13,Fin Grand Slam finals and, sensing
OL,14,Fanother opportunity at 3-3, he played
OL,15,Fa brilliant returning game, clinching
OL,16,Fhis second break with a forehand
OL,17,Fpowered into the corner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
