FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783923682
OL,3,CJannik Sinner defends Wimbledon title
OL,4,Cafter battling to defeat Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FZverev threw everything at Sinner as
OL,8,Fhe tried to serve it out, the 24-year-
OL,9,Fold at one point left sprawled on the
OL,10,Fcourt after diving for a volley.
OL,12,FBut, as he has for most of the last
OL,13,Ftwo-and-a-half years, the man from the
OL,14,FItalian mountains had the answers, and
OL,15,Fhe lay flat on his back on the turf
OL,16,Fafter powering away a final winner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
